SELECT projects.project_name, investors.investor_name, project_teams.role FROM projects JOIN project_investors ON projects.project_id = project_investors.project_id JOIN investors ON project_investors.investor_id = investors.investor_id JOIN project_teams ON projects.project_id = project_teams.project_id;

SELECT project_name, start_date, end_date, COUNT(team_member_id) AS num_team_members FROM projects JOIN project_teams ON projects.project_id = project_teams.project_id GROUP BY projects.project_id ORDER BY num_team_members DESC;
